The "schematizer" Service
=======================

This repository contains a trivial service called `schematizer`.
You can run it by doing something like

    PORT=<port> STATS_PORT=<stats_port> inenv serviceinit.d/schematizer start-dev

The documentation for this service should be available at:

    http://servicedocs.yelpcorp.com/docs/schematizer/index.html

How to Update Schematizer Docker Images to Yelp Docker Registry
============================================================================================

docker build -t docker-dev.yelpcorp.com/schematizer_service:v1 .
docker build -t docker-dev.yelpcorp.com/schematizer_database:v1 schema/
docker build -t docker-dev.yelpcorp.com/schematizer_configs:v1 acceptance/configs/

docker tag docker-dev.yelpcorp.com/schematizer_service:v1 docker-dev.yelpcorp.com/schematizer_service:latest
docker tag docker-dev.yelpcorp.com/schematizer_database:v1 docker-dev.yelpcorp.com/schematizer_database:latest
docker tag docker-dev.yelpcorp.com/schematizer_configs:v1 docker-dev.yelpcorp.com/schematizer_configs:latest
docker push docker-dev.yelpcorp.com/schematizer_service
docker push docker-dev.yelpcorp.com/schematizer_database
docker push docker-dev.yelpcorp.com/schematizer_configs

How to Get Latest Schematizer Docker Images and Set Up a Local Testing Environment
============================================================================================

docker run -d --name db docker-dev.yelpcorp.com/schematizer_database
docker run -d --name configs docker-dev.yelpcorp.com/schematizer_configs
docker run -p 8888:8888 --name schematizer --link db:schematizerdatabase --volumes-from=configs docker-dev.yelpcorp.com/schematizer_service /code/virtualenv_run/bin/python /code/serviceinit.d/schematizer start-dev

How To Service
==============

Please read the update documentation to learn more about services at Yelp,
best practices, and how to extend your service to do all the cool things
you want to do with it:

    https://trac.yelpcorp.com/wiki/HowToService
    http://servicedocs.yelpcorp.com/docs/tutorial_happyhour/index.html
